Inline CSS â€“ style={{color: 'red'}}

External CSS file â€“ import './App.css'

CSS Modules â€“ import styles from './App.module.css'

Styled Components â€“ using styled-components library

Tailwind / CSS-in-JS â€“ using utility-first or dynamic styles

4. What is the use of Parcel, Vite, Webpack?

These are bundlers/build tools that compile and optimize React apps.

Webpack â€“ powerful, configurable bundler.

Parcel â€“ zero-config bundler, fast build time.

